short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows users to switch dark themes on Google Docs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Easy Google Docs Dark Themes" allows users to easily switch between custom themes for Google Docs, including simple dark, dark purple, and other color schemes. Enhance your document editing experience with a sleek interface and personalized themes, perfect for reducing eye strain and working comfortably in different lighting conditions.
